1002503.1000851.1000867.1000964.description=Bringing along your bike just got easier. Add a locking fork bike rack to your deck rail system:
•To secure bikes in the bed: remove the front wheel, position the forks in the skewer, lock in place
•Custom-designed for Tacoma's deck rail system
•Bike rack can be positioned anywhere along the front bed rail
•Helps prevent theft and adds peace of mind
